import React from 'react'

import styles from './MyButtun.module.css'


export const MyButton = ({children, ...props}) => {

  let typeBtn

  switch (props.className) {
    case 'green-btn':
      typeBtn = styles.greenBtn
      break

    case 'active-btn':
      typeBtn = styles.activeBtn
      break

    case 'in progress-btn':
      typeBtn = styles.inprogressBtn
      break

    case 'urgent-btn':
      typeBtn = styles.urgentBtn
      break

    case 'btn-vis':
      typeBtn = styles.btnVis
      break
  
    default:
      typeBtn = styles.greenBtn
      break
  }

  const classBtn =`${typeBtn} ${styles.btn}`

  
  return (
    <button {...props} className={classBtn}>{children}</button>
  )
}
